### HTTP Request

`GET https://<%= config[:api_endpoint] %>/otp/check`

Method verifies one-time password to authorize bonuses usage on POS.

| Parameter   | Type   | Required | Description         |
|-------------|--------|----------|---------------------|
| shop_id     | String | true     | Your API key        |
| shop_secret | String | true     | Your API secret key |
| phone       | String | true     | Phone number        |
| event       | String | true     | Event to authorize  |
| code        | String | true     | Code to verify      |

On successful verification method responses with HTTP code 200.

On unsuccessful verification (wrong code or invalid parameters) method responses with HTTP code 400.
